reviews.reviewText: I divided the two bins, placing them on oppposite sides of the crib. One is for quick diaper changes and clean up. The other holds toys.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love it but doesn’t fit well on our crib
reviews.reviewText: After trying a few other caddies, this one is the perfect size for what I needed, not insanely huge or unusably small. The only thing is that it doesn’t fit nicely on cribs that have a ridge around the top because the caddy tilts downward. Nothing has fallen out yet or seems like it will but if you want that “flush” look, it might not work for you. It holds up well and stores surprisingly more than expected. Worth keeping despite the fit! And I love the color!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2022
reviews.reviewText: It’s just okay. It serves its purpose, but barely. The way it goes on, it just hangs by Velcro straps and unless it has something to rest the back on, it wants to hang practically under the changing table. It’s fine, but I wouldn’t really buy again or recommend it.
